复"}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i0.hdslb.com/bfs/face/9e4caa5d47c1e37b0bbe7f69c37a88a97733b8d0.jpg", "pendant": "", "uname": "zectal", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 1, "is_senior_member": 0, "user_sailing": null, "message": "如果赞助商的tgw物产是祥子家， 那剧情走向可能是1.祥子确实可以自由进出大豪斯，对应了第八集的关门声，只有父亲一个人被赶出来了。祥子也被下令不许与父亲有往来，祥子为了反抗家族，自己去打工。2.祥子跟家族对赌，出道家族赞助，成功的话就让父亲回家，失败就要彻底跟父亲切割关系。这也印证了猜想，银河战舰虽然大家都有点名气，但要想这么快就举办这么大型的商业演出，需要有大推手在后面。那其实核心疑点就是祥子爸到底干了什么🤔是不是入赘的大家族，然后经营投资爆雷了所以直接被驱逐了，所以祥子需要另一个商业成功来补全损失。我个人不太相信出轨说，感觉不是少女乐团番能整出来的活。拭目以待第二季[脱单doge]", "ctime": "2023-09-20 16:50:38", "like": 5, "replies": [], "sub_reply_entry_text": ""}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i0.hdslb.com/bfs/face/2a36fc7ad2268b85f1568f71a94d6e21838fd788.jpg", "pendant": "", "uname": "冰Mr", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 1, "is_senior_member": 1, "user_sailing": {"pendant": null, "cardbg": {"id": 3614, "name": "雪未来", "image": "https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/garb/item/39aa9e93217e930bbbf779a8884713896f210862.png", "jump_url": "https://www.bilibili.com/h5/mall/equity-link/home?navhide=1&item_id=3614&part=card_bg&f_source=garb&from=reply&vmid=32305341", "fan": {"is_fan": 1, "number": 66766, "color": "#67b1f6", "name": "雪未来", "num_desc": "066766"}, "type": "suit"}, "cardbg_with_focus": null}, "message": "最后一集要是能和第一集一样留下来就好了", "ctime": "2023-09-21 22:53:12", "like": 5, "replies": [], "sub_reply_entry_text": ""}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i0.hdslb.com/bfs/face/fb834bebda94767af7067788505528d0da222cc1.jpg", "pendant": "", "uname": "160422925", "current_level": 4, "vipStatus": 1, "is_senior_member": 0, "user_sailing": {"pendant": null, "cardbg": {"id": 37572, "name": "崩坏3·光辉矢愿", "image": "https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/garb/item/818686b32f2e6ce5427d9bbf05ae88f8f8360034.png", "jump_url": "https://www.bilibili.com/h5/mall/equity-link/home?navhide=1&item_id=37572&part=card_bg&f_source=garb&from=reply&vmid=1931246949", "fan": {"is_fan": 1, "number": 111179, "color": "#937ac3", "name": "崩坏3·光辉矢愿", "num_desc": "111179"}, "type": "suit"}, "cardbg_with_focus"